      485.84,
      359.8,
      588.4
    ],
    "text": "\u2022 First played in U.S.A.\u2022 5 players.\u2022 Both men and women play.\u2022 Indoor or outdoor.\u2022 Shoots a ball through a netted hoop attached to a backboard.\u2022 Time - Four quarters of 12 minutes each.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
