    ],
    "text": "Read these quotes about good sportsmanship. Add your own ideas to them and prepare a poster.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      83.18,
      139.78,
      439.34,
      170.94
    ],
    "text": "Talent wins games, but teamwork and intelligence win championships.\u201d \u2015 Michael Jordan\u2013basketball player",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      82.82,
      375.94,
      440.86,
      407.1
    ],
    "text": "\"The secret of winning football games is working more as a team, less as individuals.-Knute Rockne \u2013 American football player and coach",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      82.82,
      334.18,
      420.82,
      365.34
    ],
    "text": "One man practising sportsmanship is better than hundred teaching it.-Knute Rockne \u2013American football player and coach",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      77.32,
      262.41,
      451.78,
      323.58
    ],
    "text": "I think sportsmanship is knowing that it is a game, that we are only as good as our opponents, and whether you win or lose, to always give 100 percent. - Sue Wicks \u2013basketball player",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      83.07,
      220.38,
      267.8,
      251.54
    ],
    "text": "Just play, have fun, enjoy the game. -Michael Jordan",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      83.14,
      179.37,
      441.18,
      210.53
    ],
    "text": "Teamwork is the fuel that allows common people to produce uncommon results - Unknown",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
